"    Chalazion",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 504px; height: 378px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    A nodular lesion is present on the upper eyelid.",
